</Para>
</Commentary><Commentary id="key-bae2cf90b7420bc1ce3ca7e3afeec146" Type="F">
<Para>
<Text><CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e49865a1310" SectionRef="regulation-26-3-b-i" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/26/3/b/i">Reg. 26(3)(b)(i)</CitationSubRef> omitted (with effect in accordance with regs. 19 - 21 of the amending S.I.) by virtue of <Citation id="rnb8sic5-d3e49868a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2017" Number="725" Title="The Loans for Mortgage Interest Regulations 2017">The Loans for Mortgage Interest Regulations 2017 (S.I. 2017/725)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e49871a1310" CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e49868a1310" SectionRef="regulation-1-2-a" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/regulation/1/2/a">reg. 1(2)(a)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef id="rnb8sic5-d3e49874a1310" CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e49868a1310" SectionRef="schedule-5-paragraph-5-b" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2017/725/schedule/5/paragraph/5/b" Operative="true">Sch. 5 para. 5(b)</CitationSubRef></Text>
</Para>
</Commentary></Commentaries></Legislation>